# {{IME_PROJEKTA}} - Incident Response Center

## _traceability
- requirement: ZAH-SEC-009 Incident Response center
- design: DSN-SEC-009 Referenčna implementacija odziva na incidente
- test: TST-SEC-009 Verifikacija Incident Response primera

## Opis

Incident Response Center je enterprise-grade platforma za upravljanje varnostnih incidentov od detekcije do razrešitve, vključno z avtomatiziranimi playbooki in SOAR zmogljivostmi.

## Vključene komponente

### Incident Detection
- Alert aggregation
- Alert correlation
- False positive reduction
- Severity classification
- Automated triage

### Incident Triage
- Initial assessment
- Impact analysis
- Scope determination
- Priority assignment
- Team assignment

### Containment
- Network isolation
- Endpoint quarantine
- Account suspension
- Service shutdown
- Evidence preservation

### Eradication
- Malware removal
- Backdoor elimination
- Vulnerability patching
- Configuration hardening
- Access revocation

### Recovery
- System restoration
- Service recovery
- Data restoration
- Validation testing
- Monitoring enhancement

### Post-Incident
- Root cause analysis
- Lessons learned
- Process improvement
- Documentation
- Stakeholder communication

### SOAR Integration
- Playbook automation
- Orchestration workflows
- Third-party integration
- Case management
- Metrics tracking

